{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744970/extras/About.jpg?t=1737988835\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744970/extras/Steam_bedtime_story.jpg?t=1737988835\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grandpaw was once a brave, adventurous cat who had many tales to tell. Now, as his memories fade, all that remains is the story that was told to his beloved grandchild Lily.. and some in his old journal that has recently been discovered. It is time for you, as Lily, to go on your own quest to relive Grandpaw\u2019s adventures and uncover new ones! Can you help grandpaw remember his past? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744970/extras/Features.jpg?t=1737988835\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore Petit Island</strong>: Have the purrrfect time of your life! Discover hidden treasures and wild animals on the  island. The villages and cities have so much to offer too, so soak up all the knowledge while you can!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Capture memories</strong>: Help your grandpaw reminisce about his adventuresome days by capturing nostalgic spots on the island with your camera. Take a lot of photos with locals, tourists, animals, and everything else you can on the island!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Meet new friends and local tourists</strong>: Get to know the island's quirky and interesting characters as you go along your journey! Befriend the community to gain their trust - scratch their back, and they scratch yours!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Let yourself shine</strong>: Customize your appearance to your heart's desire! With plenty of options, you can look exactly how you want to.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744970/extras/Wishlist.gif?t=1737988835\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Visitor of Petit Island","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/92c8b9f25d4ae6ce6c3d7813db86a773afa1dc05.jpg"},{"name":"Pako the Young Prodigy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/05b7dd3398aaa55df95ac8a8442a963700bf2ada.jpg"},{"name":"Mizayaki the Legendary Fisherman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/6fd9a0be7a8782b56916d96511f09e83128973a8.jpg"},{"name":"Sandy the Green-Fingered Gardener","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/91e22bb78b5d089d7c5f8735a3109002b9ade914.jpg"},{"name":"Joe the Rival","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/1f415ab9f6854e0426efd73c45e7158c7e479a29.jpg"},{"name":"The Mysterious Guardian","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/874460413d3d1726f9bb7a4164fb0a6c30128bad.jpg"},{"name":"Tony the Old Chief","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/c1d3e54a737943d7f8cfac54b70db9c1de1db7cc.jpg"},{"name":"Donald and the Scouts","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/8a075eac571703dfab5942cc58bc67e45df41919.jpg"},{"name":"The Petit Island Scouts","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/f6ee59539209b80b6bdaa67b6751502e836e9f75.jpg"},{"name":"Volcano Island","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1744970/fd580f953b1d9e413c3e18a0c42f066b2398d6f3.jpg"}],"total":24},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamsta